text: Kostantina Pafiti (born 20 June 1995) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Cyprus women's national team. ==Career== Pafiti has been capped for the Cyprus national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Apollon Ladies F.C. players
